# Keep the build context small + clean so `railway up` uploads source only.
# (Without this, local .next/dist/node_modules bloat the context to 100s of MB
# and intermittently trip the buildkit cache-key computation on the Metal
# builder. The Dockerfiles install deps + build from source, so none of these
# are needed in the context.)
**/node_modules
**/.next
**/dist
**/.turbo
**/.git
**/.venv
**/__pycache__
**/*.log
**/coverage
**/.DS_Store
